com.google.api.gax.grpc

Class UnaryCallSettings.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.gax.grpc.UnaryCallSettings.Builder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    com.google.api.gax.grpc.UnaryCallSettingsTyped.Builder
    Enclosing class:
    UnaryCallSettings

    public static class UnaryCallSettings.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    A base builder class for UnaryCallSettings. This class cannot be used to create an instance of the abstract base class UnaryCallSettings. See the class documentation of UnaryCallSettings for a description of the different values that can be set, and for a description of when this builder may be used. Builders for concrete derived classes such as SimpleCallSettings, PagedCallSettings, or BatchingCallSettings can be used to create instances of those classes.
